title: Doldenhorn
text: The Doldenhorn is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> of the <a href="Bernese%20Alps">Bernese Alps</a>, overlooking <a href="Kandersteg">Kandersteg</a> in the <a href="Bernese%20Oberland">Bernese Oberland</a>. On its north side is <a href="Lake%20Oeschinen">Lake Oeschinen</a>.
